{"tid":2030341,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"開Game 前,不如Join一間24小時健身室。","createTime":"2020-05-22T16:29:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:01:43.000Z","uid":25568,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e5a501c86829102766c756ef57fa0b3455572000","tid":2030341,"uid":25568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:29:34.000Z","msg":"第一,有地方換衫, 24小時開放。<br />\n有廁所,可以沖涼,可以放低所有嘢。<br />\n<br />\n第二,真係私人地方,唔同喺公廁換衫,隨時畀「物件」衝入嚟。佢真係打爆啲大公司嘅門衝入去佢自己都好麻煩。呢一類型嘅健身室通常都係辦公時間先有人,其餘時間係冇職員嘅。佢想叫人開門都冇辦法。<br />\n<br />\n第三,強身健體。成日話全民勇武,但係太少人行多一步操fit自己。加入呢一類型嘅健身室,多一個安全地方。又可以操fit自己,何樂而不為。<br />\n<br />\n純屬個人意見,不喜勿插<br />\n<br />\n利申,健身jj"},{"pid":"7dd7a2b3739afea760a61e3ee8a7a10e56b36cad","tid":2030341,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:30:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b409141faa25c38ca55e12f11ec37c641a0e228e","tid":2030341,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"錢作怪"},{"pid":"bf7083c38aef848d139cfd17052de9867c06b1d1","tid":2030341,"uid":80503,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"24小時gym咁撚多cam<br />\n一個搜查令都知你係邊個"},{"pid":"7be651b43457c42d6df6be5675018032f8f53020","tid":2030341,"uid":215500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bf7083c38aef848d139cfd17052de9867c06b1d1","tid":2030341,"uid":80503,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T17:09:30.000Z","msg":"24小時gym咁撚多cam<br />\n一個搜查令都知你係